data.description: Love at first sight! This captivating home has been tastefully updated & boasts charm at every turn! High ceilings & picture windows make it feel bright & welcoming. Highlights include cozy fireplace & designer kitchen w/quarts counters, marble backsplash, pantry, bar & included SS appliances. Vaulted primary suite has custom shower & heated marble floors. Formal dinning +breakfast nook w/built-in bench & lg. bay window. Private fenced yard, garden beds & playhouse. Located just blocks from schools & park!
